by the Resolution Trust Corporation ("RTC") or from the RTC as receiver of
failed institutions.  Substantially all of these loans were sold in 1991
generating loan sale gains of approximately $14.1 million.  Because of a more
competitive market, this opportunity was not available in 1992.

