INDEPENDENT AUDITORS' CONSENT

We consent to the incorporation by reference of our opinion dated February 18,
1994 appearing in this Annual Report on Form 10-K of United Companies Financial
Corporation for the year ended December 31, 1993 in the following:
Registration Statement No. 33-15326 on Form S-8 pertaining to the United
Companies Financial Corporation 1986 Employee Incentive Stock Option Plan,
Registration Statement No. 33-17366 on Form S-8 pertaining to the United
Companies Financial Corporation Employees' Savings Plan and Trust, and
Registration Statement No. 33-29994 on Form S-8 pertaining to the 1989 Stock
Incentive Plan and the 1989 Non-Employee Director Stock Option Plan.





Baton Rouge, Louisiana
February 28, 1994





